@@ -0,0 +1,392 @@
+/**
+ * Freescale P1022RDK ALSA SoC Machine driver
+ *
+ * Author: Timur Tabi <timur@freescale.com>
+ *
+ * Copyright 2012 Freescale Semiconductor, Inc.
